review_blob: Type of beer that knocks you on your ass with a smile on your face. Very dark pour with a rich, chocolately aroma and nice orange head. The vanilla and oak chips mixed in make for a white chocolate taste. Full-bodied but with a soft finish that really brings out the bourbon favor. A must try for dark beer lovers.
beer_name: Great Divide Yeti Imperial Stout - Oak Aged
North Coast Old Rasputin Russian Imperial Stout
